    "updated_at": "2016-11-16T08:22:22Z",
    "body": "Due to the API limitation of the auto updater library we used, `autoUpdater.quitAndInstall` currently works by closing all windows first and then try to quit. And it is also too late to change the behavior since apps may already rely on it.\n\nI prefer documenting this explicitly.\n"
