    "updated_at": "2016-11-16T09:11:48Z",
    "body": "Naive question, but why can't the first line of `autoUpdater.quitAndInstall's` implementation be `app.emit('before-quit')`? That would result in less surprises and no need for doing this myself..\n\nIf that's not an option, documenting it is much still better than nothing :)\n"
