    "updated_at": "2016-11-16T09:14:21Z",
    "body": "> Naive question, but why can't the first line of autoUpdater.quitAndInstall's implementation be app.emit('before-quit')? That would result in less surprises and no need for doing this myself..\n\nAs @zcbenz it is too late to change this behavior as some apps will have been built with the current order of events in mind.  Changing the order could break existing implementations.\n"
